## FAQ

**"I'm a for-profit coding bootcamp. Do I need a license?"**  
Yes.

**"I teach at a public university. Can I use this?"**  
Yes, free under MIT.

**"I modified the code. Still need a license?"**  
If used commercially, yes.

**"Can I contribute if I have a commercial license?"**  
Absolutely.

